OL,3,C'I bleed Ratcliffe': What's next after
OL,4,Cthe power station is demolished?
OL,6,FThe clock is ticking for one of the
OL,7,FEast Midlands' most recognisable
OL,8,Flandmarks, with one worker describing
OL,9,Fthe site as being in his blood.
OL,11,FRatcliffe Power Station in - the UK's
OL,12,Flast coal-fired power station - will
OL,13,Fstop generating electricity in just
OL,14,Fthree months' time.
OL,16,FWith its eight giant cooling towers,
OL,17,Fit's been keeping the lights on across
OL,18,Fthe region since 1967.
