OL,3,C'I bleed Ratcliffe': What's next after
OL,4,Cthe power station is demolished?
OL,6,FOn September 30, the powers station
OL,7,Fwill close for good, and the use of
OL,8,Fcoal to produce electricity in this
OL,9,Fcountry will end.
OL,11,FIn an interview with ITV News Central,
OL,12,Felectrical engineer John Roberts
OL,13,Fdescribed the site as fantastic.
OL,15,F'It's in my blood...I bleed Ratcliffe'
OL,17,FHe joined as an apprentice 44 years
OL,18,Fago, and will retire when production
OL,19,Fstops in the autumn.
