OL,3,C'I bleed Ratcliffe': What's next after
OL,4,Cthe power station is demolished?
OL,6,FJohn said: "It's in my blood, you cut
OL,7,Fme out, I bleed Ratcliffe"
OL,9,FHe added: "A bit of sadness, to me
OL,10,Fit's an adults Meccano Set. It's
OL,11,Fgreat, just fantastic. The grass is
OL,12,Fnot greener anywhere else."
OL,14,FConstruction work on the plant began
OL,15,Fin 1963. Four years later it was up
OL,16,Fand running.
