OL,6,FIt can power two million homes, and
OL,7,Fhas the capacity to generate 2000
OL,8,Fmegawatts of electricity. Enough over
OL,9,Fits lifetime to make 21 trillion cups
OL,10,Fof tea.
OL,12,FFor many of the staff, Ratcliffe has
OL,13,Fbeen their life.
OL,15,FPlant manager Peter O'Grady told ITV
OL,16,FNews Central: "I reflect back on when
OL,17,FI started.
