OL,6,FChris Bellaby joined the team straight
OL,7,Fout of university. While Angela
OL,8,FMillward has seen a lot of changes in
OL,9,Fher 29 years on site.JIn an interview
OL,10,Fwith ITV Central Angela said: "I
OL,11,Fstarted as a teenager fresh from
OL,12,Fcollege doing engineering. Worked
OL,13,Fthrough multiple different roles and
OL,14,Factivities.
OL,16,F"Met my husband here, had two
OL,17,Fchildren, one of which is also
OL,18,Fspending time here now. So it's
OL,19,Fdefinitely part of the family.
