OL,3,C'I bleed Ratcliffe': What's next after
OL,4,Cthe power station is demolished?
OL,6,FChris said: Very sad to see it go.
OL,7,FSome of the memories, some of the team
OL,8,Fmates, friends that we've made here,
OL,9,Fand hopefully friendships long-lasting.
OL,11,F"But we've got to look to the future,
OL,12,Fwe're all proud of the role we've
