OL,3,C'I bleed Ratcliffe': What's next after
OL,4,Cthe power station is demolished?
OL,6,FMore than a 100 staff will stay on to
OL,7,Fdecommission the plant. A process
OL,8,Fwhich will take two years.
OL,10,FAmong them is Akhil Moonukandathil, he
OL,11,Fwill help to decontaminate the site in
OL,12,Fpreparation for whatever takes its
OL,13,Fplace.JAkhil says: "I'll be doing
OL,14,Fsomething very different to what I've
OL,15,Fbeen doing so far. So far I've been
OL,16,Finstalling new things or mending
OL,17,Fthings.
