OL,6,F"But moving forward we'll be
OL,7,Fdisconnecting, making it ready for a
OL,8,Fdemolition contractor to eventually
OL,9,Fdemolish this place."
OL,11,FWhat's next?JThe site owners are
OL,12,FUniper, a German multinational energy
OL,13,Fcompany.JIn an interview with ITV News
OL,14,FCentral, Uniper CEO Michael Lewis
OL,15,Fsaid: "We're looking at whether there
OL,16,Fcould be green hydrogen production on
OL,17,Fthis site for industry in the East
OL,18,FMidlands.
