OL,6,F"And one of the things hydrogen is
OL,7,Fparticularly important for is seasonal
OL,8,Fstorage, so that we can take excess
OL,9,Fproduction of renewables and turn it
OL,10,Finto flexible power when it's needed."
OL,11,FBefore then, the famous cooling towers
OL,12,F- each 114 metres in height - will
OL,13,Fhave to come tumbling down.
OL,15,FThis is expected to happen some time
OL,16,Faround 2030.
